  "text": "We included dummy variables for the 11 planning and service areas used by Florida agencies. The largest planning and service area (Region 11) serves South Florida (Dade and Monroe counties) and is the excluded baseline reference region. We included the Medicaid bed occupancy rate for nursing homes in the enrollee's county in the model predicting nursing home days, because the availability of nursing home beds can be a predictor of low use of HCBS alternatives [CITATION_1] .",
